data.description: Looking for a place to spread out and relax? Longing to hear whippoorwills while watching the catfish jump? Look no farther than this lakefront home built for entertaining. Choose between the expansive porches that welcomes you home, the rooftop deck that beckons you to view the lake, or bask in the sun on the large pier. Almost 3500 sqft of decking! The calm, deep water canal is perfect for paddle boarding & doesn't experience the harsh waves that come with open water. Even at low lake levels, you can still get your boat out. The shoreline is protected with 230' of seawall. The large boathouse closet has room for all your toys. The lake pump and movable irrigation lines ensure green grass with low water bills. Ample parking, dual primary bedrooms, & an expansive lawn with St Augustine grass make this home an entertainers dream. Whether you are looking for part or full time living, this home offers year round comfort & entertainment. Furniture negotiable. Seller offering 2-1 Buydown. 2023-10-26
